{"tid":1015671,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 - 話梅豬手","createTime":"2019-02-10T08:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T08:27:48.000Z","uid":30742,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c5ad82a31e347296052ee8f54ab6e983d65d5369","tid":1015671,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T08:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt9Wun3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt9Wun3.jpg&h=3c4c6a89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Up-0yd7Uwvw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUp-0yd7Uwvw&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BGmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=8d514f87\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Up-0yd7Uwvw</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個係之前有位巴打點菜既！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁岩之前做自家團年想整豬手，但天氣太熱想整d酸酸甜甜既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (本來係想整豬肚雞既，但真係太熱喇！)！<br />\n就做左話梅豬手！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個既簡單又好味！ 基本上係一定100％成功！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n煮完某人連話梅都清埋！係咁話多d肉就好&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而呢個亦係我老媽相當喜歡既一個餸！佢都係無酸甜不歡！<br />\n我估應該無咩女仔唔鍾意酸甜吧？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n圖文食譜 <a href=\"https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2019/02/braised-pork-knuckle-with-dried-sweet.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F02%2Fbraised-pork-knuckle-with-dried-sweet.html&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BGmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=d70830b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2019/02/braised-pork-knuckle-with-dried-sweet.html</a><br />\nFacebook專頁 : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BGmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=d7014699\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BGmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=54c6bcee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BGmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=a27909d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"8aeb7fa3b0f8788008e317f33f793dd3bd34e238","tid":1015671,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T08:02:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b08ba09f5211eff5955fceb5fcddc2b44b383f","tid":1015671,"uid":76710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T08:12:14.000Z","msg":"下次整花生紋豬尾囉"},{"pid":"664532318a0d61a88f19aac810f1531cf2493075","tid":1015671,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4b08ba09f5211eff5955fceb5fcddc2b44b